		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Every NES shipped with Super Mario Bros. They decided A = jump. Everyone got used to that. Other games copied this to fit in with user expectations.<br /><br />Edit. The only game I can think of that maps B to jump is Ooze, from Action 52.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
